[I] An anonymous Internet communication system

[T] Tor is a toolset for a wide range of organizations and people that want to
[T] improve their safety and security on the Internet. Using Tor can help you
[T] anonymize web browsing and publishing, instant messaging, IRC, SSH, and
[T] more.

